main event: A report on a UFO sighting involving multiple jets that tracked an unidentified flying object on radar for 28 minutes on May 23, 1967.
interesting points: The object was described as having variable shape, color, size, and speed., It was tracked on radar by 6 jets., The object disappeared rapidly at various times., The observer noted seeing bright green lights associated with the object., The sky was clear and starry at the time of observation.
sighted object: unidentified flying object emitting bright green lights
witness description: a housewife and a part-time college student, both deemed reliable
